%% 3.2.6 Register Face ID — sequence
%% POST /api/FaceRecognition/RegisterStudentFace multipart
%% BR45: Clear image, single face — validated by CompreFace / service

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant FC as FaceRecognitionController
    participant FS as FaceRecognitionService
    participant CF as CompreFace API
    participant Repo as IRepository Student
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Update Face ID — grant camera permission
    App->>App: Capture face photo
    App->>FC: POST /api/FaceRecognition/RegisterStudentFace form-data studentId + file
    FC->>FS: RegisterStudentFaceAsync
    FS->>Repo: Verify student exists
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    FS->>CF: POST recognition faces (subject)
    CF-->>FS: OK
    FS-->>FC: subject name
    FC-->>App: 200 OK
    App->>Guardian: Face enrollment successful
